              "html": "<div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; \" > <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SOzXu33qFMo\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen style=\" position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \"></iframe> </div>\n<p>Here's an experimental verification of the theoretical probability given in the last post: <a href=\"https://willward.netlify.app/stat110-ch1-poker-hand-probabilities/\">Poker Hand Probabilities: One Pair</a></p>",
